     "t": "These sensations - the expansive mind, the open chest, the quiet ease of allowing yourself to imagine something better - are the physiological signatures of being in relationship with your vision. They are evidence that your psychology is doing its job: translating possibility into the form of beliefs, thoughts and emotions, where they’re one step closer to becoming action."
